BODY:

-00 civic front end.

-black housing jdm headlights.

-type r grill.

-front and rear jdm bumper lips.

-99-00 civic tail lights.

-vis carbon fiber hood.

INTERIOR:

-dad swade front seats.

-00 civic si steering wheel.(leather)

-pioneer 600 watt amplifier.

-pioneer mp3 player stereo 60w x 4.(deh-p80mp).

-geddy turbo timer.

-autometer boost and pyrometer gauges.

-autometer shift light.

SUSPENSION:

-rear disc brake conversion.

-brembo cross drilled rotors with axis brake pads.

-front upper strut bar,rear upper strut bar and rear lower stru bar.

-full 2000 civic si suspension and brake system including sway bars.

- koni full coil overs set.

- front and rear ingalls camber kit.

WHEELS:

- 17" rev wheels with 205-40-17 tires.(a week old)

ENGINE:

-engine management is microtech lt-8s.

-ls block( 1.8 ) with b16 head.

-head is ported and polished with a 3 angle valve job.its got crane springs and retainers and crower valves.

-block has srp 9:5 compression ,bored10 over. 

-str block guard.

-eagle rods.

-arp head studs.

-gsr cams.

-cometic head gasket.

-aem cam gears.

-aem fuelpressure regulator and fuel rail.

-precission 880cc injectors.

-jg edelbrock victor x intake manifold.

-bbk 70mm throtle body.

-msd ignition coil.

-msd spark plug wires.

- walbro 255 in t6ank fuel pump.

TRANSMISSION:

-ls transmission.

-quaife limited slip differential(lsd).

-clutch masters stage 5 clutch kit.

-gator racing axles stage 3 .

TURBO:

-turbonetics t3/t4 hybrid.

-greedy intercoler kit.

-blitz blow off valve.

-turbonetics wastegate.

-blox turbo manifold.

-custom 3"downpipe.

-thermal 3"exhaust system.

Hægan  hægan,,,, 

Ef menn myndu nenna að lesa þá kemur fram að í vélinni eru SRP stimplar, sem Flatlander Racing framleiðir eftir óskum viðskiptavinarinns. 

Þannig að það eru sér smíðaðir stimplar í þessari vél. 

Ynnihaldið í þessari vél er að mér sýnist allt alvöru.
